  {
    "client_msg_id": "6d013660-6d40-4065-810f-84b89da0f39b",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "What I like is the fast 'cross cutting connection' light up on hover. Mostly I am chasing the connection between two sofware regions and something like that may work. The execution is fun to watch but when everything flickers you can't tell any patterns. What if everything didn't flicker though? Or if you had a way to only show you the executions that match a specific condition?",
